OL,3,CArtists facing 'cost-of-touring
OL,4,Ccrisis', warn MPs in call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FArtists are facing a "cost-of-touring
OL,8,Fcrisis" and venues are stopping live
OL,9,Fmusic or closing entirely at a rate of
OL,10,Ftwo per week, a report into grassroots
OL,11,Fmusic venues has found.
OL,13,FFestivals, electronic music venues,
OL,14,Facademies and arenas "are not
OL,15,Finsulated from the impacts" of the
OL,16,Fcrisis and "promoters are less able to
OL,17,Fput on shows or make them financially
OL,18,Fviable", it said.
