OL,3,CArtists facing 'cost-of-touring
OL,4,Ccrisis', warn MPs in call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe report, focusing on immediate
OL,8,Fsolutions to support grassroots music,
OL,9,Falso calls for a temporary VAT cut
OL,10,Fbased on venue capacity to "stimulate
OL,11,Fgrassroots music activity and help the
OL,12,Fsector through the current closure
OL,13,Fcrisis".
OL,15,FThe committee has recommended a
OL,16,Fwidespread voluntary levy to be in
OL,17,Fplace no later than September, which
OL,18,Fshould be followed with an
OL,19,Feffectiveness assessment by the
OL,20,FGovernment.
OL,26,@rD@\OUuD@GO]
