OL,3,CArtists facing 'cost-of-touring
OL,4,Ccrisis', warn MPs in call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FIt said the levy on arena and stadium
OL,8,Fconcert tickets, which would create a
OL,9,Fsupport fund for venues, artists and
OL,10,Fpromoters, should not be passed on to
OL,11,Fmusic fans.
OL,13,FThe committee also said a trust led by
OL,14,Fa sector umbrella body, such as the
OL,15,FLive Trust or Music Venues Trust
OL,16,F(MVT), would be the best way to
OL,17,Fcollect, manage and distribute the
OL,18,Fvoluntary fund.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/10
