OL,3,CArtists facing 'cost-of-touring
OL,4,Ccrisis', warn MPs in call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FThe report added that if there is no
OL,8,Fagreement by September, or if it fails
OL,9,Fto collect enough income to support
OL,10,Fthe sector, the Government should step
OL,11,Fin and introduce a statutory levy.
OL,13,FDame Caroline Dinenage, chairwoman of
OL,14,Fthe committee, said: "We are grateful
OL,15,Fto the many dedicated local venues who
OL,16,Fgave up their time to take part in our
OL,17,Finquiry.
OL,19,F"They delivered the message loud and
OL,20,Fclear that grassroots music venues are
OL,21,Fin crisis.
