OL,3,CArtists facing 'cost-of-touring
OL,4,Ccrisis', warn MPs in call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"The ongoing wave of closures is not
OL,8,Fjust a disaster for music, performers
OL,9,Fand supporters in local communities up
OL,10,Fand down the country, but also puts at
OL,11,Frisk the entire live music ecosystem.
OL,13,F"If the grassroots, where musicians,
OL,14,Ftechnicians, tour managers and
OL,15,Fpromoters hone their craft, are
OL,16,Fallowed to wither and die, the UK's
OL,17,Fposition as a music powerhouse faces a
OL,18,Fbleak future.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
