OL,3,CArtists facing 'cost-of-touring
OL,4,Ccrisis', warn MPs in call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"To stem the overwhelming, ongoing
OL,8,Ftide of closures, we urgently need a
OL,9,Flevy on arena and stadium concert
OL,10,Ftickets to fund financial support for
OL,11,Fthe sector, alongside a VAT cut to
OL,12,Fhelp get more shows into venues.
OL,14,F"While the current focus is on the
OL,15,Fmany grassroots music venues falling
OL,16,Fsilent, those working in the live
OL,17,Fmusic sector across the board are also
OL,18,Funder extraordinary strain.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
