OL,3,CArtists facing 'cost-of-touring
OL,4,Ccrisis', warn MPs in call for more
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"It is time that the Government
OL,8,Fbrought together everyone with a stake
OL,9,Fin the industry's success, including
OL,10,Fmusic fans, to address the long-term
OL,11,Fchallenges and ensure live music can
OL,12,Fthrive into the future."
OL,14,FMark Davyd, chief executive and
OL,15,Ffounder of the MVT, welcomed the
OL,16,Ffindings and thanked the committee for
OL,17,Fits recommendations.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@XO]
