OL,7,FHe said: "It has taken much longer
OL,8,Fthan any of us would have liked to get
OL,9,Fthe positive change we all wanted to
OL,10,Fsee, but we could not have achieved
OL,11,Fthis fantastic outcome without your
OL,12,Fcontinued support for your local live
OL,13,Fmusic venue."
OL,15,FJon Collins, chief executive of Live,
OL,16,Falso welcomed the "knowledgeable and
OL,17,Fwide-ranging" report.
OL,26,@oD@JOUuD@MO]xD@SOUyD@MO]
