OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"It's clear that the committee has
OL,8,Frecognised the many challenges faced
OL,9,Fby venues, promoters, events and
OL,10,Fartists at the grassroots level, and
OL,11,Fthe steps required to address them",
OL,12,Fhe said.
OL,14,FMr Collins added that Live is looking
OL,15,Fforward to working with the Government
OL,16,Fon the review of VAT.
